create a django project
inside the created project, create an app
in the project settings file, install the app
inside the app folder, create a urls file

in the project urls, import iclude (from django.urls import path, include)

create a default url/path and include your app's urls file
in the app urls file, within the urls pattern, create a default path/urls and specify the function !don't forget to import views!

(from django.urls import path
from . import views

urlpatterns = [

    path('', views.home)

]
)

in the views files, define the functions referenced in the app urls
